**File:** `/Users/mike/github/sw-embed/sw-cor24-x-tinyc/components/frontend/crates/tc24r-lexer/src/readers.rs` (lines 219-254)

This function maps string keywords to `TokenKind` variants. Currently matches `"const"`, `"static"`, `"extern"`, `"inline"`, etc. You need to add the new keywords here:

